    <title>Pony Bot</title>
    <updated>2016-03-31T00:00:00+02:00</updated>
    <content type="html">&lt;section id="pony-bot"&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A robo-pet&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="project-thumb"&gt;
&lt;a class="reference external image-reference" href="/_images/545571460052755967.jpg"&gt;&lt;img alt="projects/project-10665/images/545571460052755967.jpg" src="projects/project-10665/images/545571460052755967.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a class="reference external image-reference" href="/_images/1182321459443040787.jpg"&gt;&lt;img alt="projects/project-10665/images/1182321459443040787.jpg" src="projects/project-10665/images/1182321459443040787.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a class="reference external image-reference" href="/_images/1641971459443030083.jpg"&gt;&lt;img alt="projects/project-10665/images/1641971459443030083.jpg" src="projects/project-10665/images/1641971459443030083.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a class="reference external image-reference" href="/_images/7796781460658379406.jpg"&gt;&lt;img alt="projects/project-10665/images/7796781460658379406.jpg" src="projects/project-10665/images/7796781460658379406.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a class="reference external image-reference" href="/_images/6895731474292178584.jpg"&gt;&lt;img alt="projects/project-10665/images/6895731474292178584.jpg" src="projects/project-10665/images/6895731474292178584.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a class="reference external image-reference" href="/_images/5602221462630824844.jpg"&gt;&lt;img alt="projects/project-10665/images/5602221462630824844.jpg" src="projects/project-10665/images/5602221462630824844.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight-none notranslate"&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;This is yet another attempt at a 8-servo walking robot, similar to {ref}`project-6321`  and {ref}`project-8521` . Except this time I want it to be a cute robot pet, so I had to
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;choose a cute shape for it. I will need to make yet another breakout
board for the servos (the one I used on µKatka has some flaws) and
this time I will need some sensors – not sure what yet.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section id="logs"&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Logs&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul class="postlist-style-none postlist simple"&gt;
&lt;li class="ablog-post"&gt;&lt;p class="ablog-post-title"&gt;2017-09-19 - &lt;a class="reference internal" href="../../../projects/project-10665/log-67467/"&gt;Trinket M0&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class="ablog-post"&gt;&lt;p class="ablog-post-title"&gt;2016-09-19 - &lt;a class="reference internal" href="../../../projects/project-10665/log-45764/"&gt;Better Servo Mounts&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class="ablog-post"&gt;&lt;p class="ablog-post-title"&gt;2016-09-12 - &lt;a class="reference internal" href="../../../projects/project-10665/log-45486/"&gt;New Brain&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class="ablog-post"&gt;&lt;p class="ablog-post-title"&gt;2016-09-10 - &lt;a class="reference internal" href="../../../projects/project-10665/log-45384/"&gt;Some Code&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class="ablog-post"&gt;&lt;p class="ablog-post-title"&gt;2016-05-07 - &lt;a class="reference internal" href="../../../projects/project-10665/log-37620/"&gt;Schematic&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class="ablog-post"&gt;&lt;p class="ablog-post-title"&gt;2016-05-06 - &lt;a class="reference internal" href="../../../projects/project-10665/log-37560/"&gt;Brains&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class="ablog-post"&gt;&lt;p class="ablog-post-title"&gt;2016-04-14 - &lt;a class="reference internal" href="../../../projects/project-10665/log-35926/"&gt;Servos, Horns and Screws&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class="ablog-post"&gt;&lt;p class="ablog-post-title"&gt;2016-04-14 - &lt;a class="reference internal" href="../../../projects/project-10665/log-35887/"&gt;Attaching Servos to the Body&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class="ablog-post"&gt;&lt;p class="ablog-post-title"&gt;2016-04-07 - &lt;a class="reference internal" href="../../../projects/project-10665/log-35405/"&gt;New Legs&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class="ablog-post"&gt;&lt;p class="ablog-post-title"&gt;2016-04-06 - &lt;a class="reference internal" href="../../../projects/project-10665/log-35305/"&gt;Controller PCB&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class="ablog-post"&gt;&lt;p class="ablog-post-title"&gt;2016-03-31 - &lt;a class="reference internal" href="../../../projects/project-10665/log-34972/"&gt;Servo Mounting Holes&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
